1. Rebuild [Watch](file:///C:/GoLive/new%20UI/src/pages/Watch.tsx#11-135), [Studio](file:///C:/GOLive/app/studio/page.tsx#10-164), and [Search](file:///C:/GoLive/new%20UI/src/pages/Search.tsx#6-106) pages to match the new UI's premium style.
